Procedure*Text: In this section, you will be presented with a series of words. Please study each word carefully. Your memory will be tested!

A rating of 0 = WILL NOT REMEMBER, while a rating of 100 = WILL DEFINITELY REMEMBER. Please try to be as accurate as possible with these ratings!
